## 🧪 API Endpoints

### Create Ride
POST /api/rides

### Assign Driver
POST /api/rides/{rideId}/assign-driver

### Start Ride
POST /api/rides/{rideId}/start

### Complete Ride
POST /api/rides/{rideId}/complete

### Cancel Ride
POST /api/rides/{rideId}/cancel

